   <p>Proposed budget for 1912-13 - no income presented).</p>
   <p>Disbursements.</p>
   <table>
    <row>
     <cell>Salary, Rabbi</cell>
     <cell>$15,000.00</cell>
    </row>
    <row>
     <cell>Extra Compensation</cell>
     <cell>5,000.00</cell>
    </row>
    <row>
     <cell>Financial Secretary</cell>
     <cell>1,500.00</cell>
    </row>
    <row>
     <cell>Janitor and Assistants</cell>
     <cell>1,500.00</cell>
    </row>
    <row>
     <cell>Engineer and Fireman</cell>
     <cell>2,200.00</cell>
    </row>
    <row>
